.TH webp-man 1  "man " 
.SH NAME
man \- Print a man page in roff, for `man \-l \-` or a package\*(Aqs man directory
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBman\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fICOMMAND\fR] 
